---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="gradient-text">About Me</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm a <strong class="text-white">Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</strong> student with a deep passion for building mobile applications. My journey in tech is driven by curiosity and the desire to create apps that make a difference.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm particularly interested in <strong class="text-space-glow">cross-platform mobile development</strong> using Flutter/Dart. Every project is an opportunity to learn something new and push my boundaries.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          When I'm not coding, I'm exploring new technologies, learning about UI/UX design principles, and thinking about how to build apps that people genuinely enjoy using.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600/20 to-cyan-500/20 border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center space-y-4 p-8">
            <div class="text-6xl font-heading font-bold gradient-text">BSCS</div>
            <div class="text-slate-400">Computer Science Student</div>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 pt-4">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 border border-purple-500/30">Flutter</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-300 border border-cyan-500/30">Java</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 border border-emerald-500/30">Mobile Dev</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
